The body of a missing Parktown Boys High pupil has been found. Gauteng's education MEC confirmed the finding. Education MEC Panyaza Lesufi says the department will provide counselling for Mpianzi's family. JOHANNESBURG - Gauteng Education MEC Panyaza Lesufi briefs the media after 13-year-old Enoch Mpianzi's body was found in North West. He had gone missing during a water activity as part of a school camp hosted by Parktown Boys' High. READ: Body of missing Parktown Boys pupil found The body was found by police.